com.b2international.snowowl.datastore

Class CDOEditingContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.CDOEditingContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseSnomedEditingContext

    public abstract class CDOEditingContext
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    This class is a thin, generic wrapper around the underlying CDOTransaction. In order to make it terminology independent, it uses EObjects as opposed to specific classes.
